<p>Looking good: The Love Island star flaunted her curves in a pair of tiny denim shorts and a skin-tight black top</p>

<p>Belle left Love Island in a couple with Anton Danyluk, 24, but the pair split just five weeks after exiting the villa. </p>

<p>Since then Belle has been linked to Absolutely Ascot's Rudi Hewitt with the pair being spotted on a date in August, reports the Sun.</p>

<p>However the blonde beauty hasn't made the rumoured romance Instagram official, instead opting to share sizzling selfies and sexy lingerie shots. </p>

